Bug on SVGPaint implementation Batik1.5beta5
SVGPaint.setPaint doesn't work, it doesn't update the property

ex:
SVGStylable svgStylable = (SVGStylable)element;
CSSStyleDeclaration cssStyle = svgStylable.getStyle();
SVGPaint p = (SVGPaint)cssStyle.getPropertyCSSValue("fill");
p.setPaint(SVGPaint.SVG_PAINTTYPE_URI,newUri,null, null); // this is not
updating the value
System.out.println(p.getPaintType()); // it doesn't show the value of 107 which
is SVG_PAINTTYPE_URI
